{
  "name": "几何集合动画预设",
  "description": "动态几何图形动画，包含多种形状的浮动效果",
  "kind": "iframe",
  "align": "right",
  "html": "<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset='utf-8'/><style>html,body{margin:0;padding:0;width:100%;height:100%;overflow:hidden;font-family:system-ui,sans-serif;color:#fff;background:transparent}.container{position:relative;width:100%;height:100%;padding:15px 20px;box-sizing:border-box;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:flex-end}.geometric-bg{position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;z-index:0}.shape{position:absolute;opacity:0.4;animation:float 8s infinite ease-in-out}.circle{border-radius:50%;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(255,105,180,0.3),transparent 70%)}.square{border-radius:8px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(0,191,255,0.3),rgba(30,144,255,0.2))}.triangle{width:0;height:0;border-left:25px solid transparent;border-right:25px solid transparent;border-bottom:43px solid rgba(50,205,50,0.3);background:none}@keyframes float{0%,100%{transform:translate(0,0) rotate(0deg)}50%{transform:translate(10px,-15px) rotate(180deg)}}.content-panel{position:relative;z-index:1;background:rgba(15,20,30,0.9);backdrop-filter:blur(15px);border-radius:14px;padding:18px 22px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);box-shadow:0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);max-width:380px;min-width:300px}.panel-header{display:flex;align-items:center;margin-bottom:12px}.geo-icon{width:32px;height:32px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff69b4,#00bfff);border-radius:8px;margin-right:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:16px;animation:rotate 6s infinite linear}.geo-icon span{transform:rotate(-45deg)}@keyframes rotate{0%{transform:rotate(0deg)}100%{transform:rotate(360deg)}}.header-text{flex:1}.title{font-size:20px;font-weight:700;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#ff69b4,#00bfff);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text;margin-bottom:2px}.tag{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#00bfff;font-weight:600}.description{font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;opacity:0.9;margin-bottom:16px}.features{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:10px;margin-bottom:16px}.feature-item{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border-radius:8px;padding:10px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08)}.feature-title{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:4px}.feature-desc{font-size:10px;opacity:0.7;line-height:1.3}.status{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1)}.status-dot{width:6px;height:6px;background:#00ff88;border-radius:50%;animation:pulse 2s infinite}@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:0.5}}.status-text{font-size:11px;opacity:0.8}.time{font-size:10px;opacity:0.6}</style></head><body><div class='container'><div class='geometric-bg' id='geoContainer'></div><div class='content-panel'><div class='panel-header'><div class='geo-icon'><span>◈</span></div><div class='header-text'><div class='title'>几何动画预设</div><div class='tag'>GEOMETRIC PRESET</div></div></div><div class='description'>动态几何图形动画效果，适合科技展示和创意直播场景。</div><div class='features'><div class='feature-item'><div class='feature-title'>动态图形</div><div class='feature-desc'>多种几何形状浮动动画</div></div><div class='feature-item'><div class='feature-title'>渐变色彩</div><div class='feature-desc'>彩虹渐变配色方案</div></div><div class='feature-item'><div class='feature-title'>3D效果</div><div class='feature-desc'>CSS 3D变换动画</div></div><div class='feature-item'><div class='feature-title'>实时交互</div><div class='feature-desc'>鼠标悬停响应效果</div></div></div><div class='status'><div style='display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px'><div class='status-dot'></div><div class='status-text'>动画运行中</div></div><div class='time' id='timeDisplay'>15:30</div></div></div></div><script>function updateTime(){const e=new Date,t=e.getHours().toString().padStart(2,'0'),o=e.getMinutes().toString().padStart(2,'0');document.getElementById('timeDisplay').textContent=`${t}:${o}`}function createGeometry(){const e=document.getElementById('geoContainer'),t=['circle','square','triangle'],o=['rgba(255,105,180,0.25)','rgba(0,191,255,0.25)','rgba(50,205,50,0.25)','rgba(255,215,0,0.25)','rgba(138,43,226,0.25)'];for(let n=0;n<10;n++){const a=document.createElement('div');a.className=`shape ${t[Math.floor(Math.random()*t.length)]}`;const r=Math.random()*60+20,i=Math.random()*100,l=Math.random()*100,c=Math.random()*6+4,d=Math.random()*2,s=o[Math.floor(Math.random()*o.length)];a.style.width=`${r}px`,a.style.height=`${r}px`,a.style.left=`${i}%`,a.style.top=`${l}%`,a.style.animationDelay=`${d}s`,a.style.animationDuration=`${c}s`,a.className.includes('triangle')?(a.style.width='0',a.style.height='0',a.style.borderLeft=`${r/2}px solid transparent`,a.style.borderRight=`${r/2}px solid transparent`,a.style.borderBottom=`${r}px solid ${s}`,a.style.background='none'):a.className.includes('circle')?a.style.background=`radial-gradient(circle,${s},transparent 70%)`:a.style.background=s,e.appendChild(a)}}document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded',function(){updateTime(),createGeometry(),setInterval(updateTime,6e4);const e=document.querySelector('.content-panel');e.addEventListener('mouseenter',function(){this.style.transform='translateY(-2px)',this.style.boxShadow='0 15px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.7),0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.2)'}),e.addEventListener('mouseleave',function(){this.style.transform='translateY(0)',this.style.boxShadow='0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.6)'})});</script></body></html>",
  "extraCss": ".lt-root { justify-content: flex-end !important; padding: 5vh 6vw !important; } .lt-container { min-width: 380px !important; max-width: 450px !important; }"
}